<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Til O'rganamiz (Rus/Yapon)</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4A90E2;
            --secondary: #50E3C2;
            --dark: #2C3E50;
            --light: #F4F7F6;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f4037 0%, #99f2c8 100%);
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 30px 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--dark);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1565c0;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: #fff3e0;
            border-left: 5px solid #ff9800;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #e65100;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--dark);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background: white;
        }

        input:focus,
        select:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            outline: none;
        }

        .btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), #357ABD);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Poliqlot - Til Markazi 🌍</h2>

        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>💡 Tavsiya qilingan maslahat:</strong> Har qanday tilni o'rganish sabr talab etadi. Kuniga uzluksiz
            shug'ullanish orqali:<br>
            • <b>30 daqiqa:</b> 6 oyda o'rtacha gaplasha olasiz.<br>
            • <b>60 daqiqa:</b> 3-4 oyda yaxshi so'zlashasiz!
        </div>

        <div class="warning-box">
            ⚠️ Yodda tuting: Darslik jarayoni orqada yopilib qolmasligi uchun vaqtingiz tugamaguncha sahifadan
            tashqariga chiqa olmaysiz!
        </div>

        <form action="/register" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="ism">Ismingiz</label>
                <input type="text" id="ism" name="ism" required placeholder="Masalan: Sardor">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="telefon">Telefon raqamingiz</label>
                <input type="text" id="telefon" name="telefon" required placeholder="+998901234567">
            </div>

            <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                <div class="form-group" style="flex: 1;">
                    <label for="lang">Qaysi tilni o'rganasiz?</label>
                    <select name="lang" id="lang" required>
                        <option value="ru">Rus tili 🇷🇺</option>
                        <option value="ja">Yapon tili 🇯🇵</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group" style="flex: 1;">
                    <label for="daily_goal">Kunlik vaqt:</label>
                    <select name="daily_goal" id="daily_goal" required>
                        <option value="1">1 daqiqa (Test)</option>
                        <option value="15">15 daqiqa</option>
                        <option value="30" selected>30 daqiqa</option>
                        <option value="60">60 daqiqa</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn">Darsni Boshlash 🚀</button>
        </form>
    </div>

</body>

</html>